<package name="mate-applet-softupd" project="openSUSE:Factory">
  <title>MATE panel applet for software update notifications</title>
  <description>This is a MATE panel applet to notify when software updates are available.

The notification is displayed in two ways:
  1) by changing the icon of the applet.
  2) by sending a notification to the notification-daemon.

The information is obtained from PackageKit.</description>
  <devel project="X11:MATE:Factory" package="mate-applet-softupd"/>
</package>
